Prosper Loans Analysis¶

TOC:¶

  • Dataset Overview.
  • Questions that we are trying to answer.
  • Extracting Data.
  • Assessing And Cleaning.
  • Visulaizations.
    • Univariate Visuals:
      • Loans Distribuation.
      • Months' distribution.
      • State Distribution.
    • Bivariate Visuals:
      • Relation between Income Range and Loans categories.
      • Relation Between Borrowers State and Loans Categories.
      • Relation Between Income Range and Prosper Score.
    • Multivariate Visuals:
      • Relation Between Income Range and Debt to Income Ratio And Number Of Open Credit Lines.
      • Relation Between Borrowers Occupation and Dept To Income Ratio and Prosper Score.
      • Relation Between Prosper Score And Number Of open Credit lines and Employment status.

Dataset Overview:

The dataset we have is about prosper loans for a bank which describes everyhing about loans of the borrowers like theire pupose or loan category and also information about the borrower itself.

What Questions that we will Answer?

  • What Category of loans is the most ordered?
  • What is the most familiar months that the borrowers make loans?
  • What state has the most number of loans?
  • What is the most employment status that ordered a loan?
  • What is the relation between Open Credit lines and both Income Range and Debit to Income Ratio?
  • Income ranges of the borrowers ?
